{"tid":361220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣大停電，經濟部長請辭","createTime":"2017-08-16T02:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T03:46:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e46fcb4864a94e467b06fb29323f0f12dcfb443","tid":361220,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/103238_3a65f259fb2c7448285da53307ecbf55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F103238_3a65f259fb2c7448285da53307ecbf55.jpg&h=3ce509b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕昨天全台大停電，經濟部長李世光請辭下台獲准，行政院發言人徐國勇今天（16日）表示，目前辭呈還未送到，預計上午11點會送達行政院長林全，並確定經濟部長將由經濟部次長沈榮津暫時代理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2164416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2164416&d=hQVzQDzE8chcMGTb1XN0%2B26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8c8d276f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2164416&h=b569ed07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2164416</a>"},{"pid":"eaba6be82d1712475ad7efe4992fe598b25afd1d","tid":361220,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:37:58.000Z","msg":"香港：要官員辭職係對官員嘅侮辱"},{"pid":"cc9509de636495938aedf0abac5802b33fa530bb","tid":361220,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"平時班踩台支那狗唔見晒影"},{"pid":"957b567fc36e9688209714064e10cacc4f711133","tid":361220,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:49:00.000Z","msg":"睇下台灣幾文明, 香港真係仆街"},{"pid":"e75cb980368a87fc2ba5d653d13425eefab547ed","tid":361220,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:43:04.000Z","msg":"香港：機器故障要官員下台簡直天方夜譚"},{"pid":"ba710a199002e6ed536235b6c0ad